node.text:
The Anniversary Package is officially on sale from now for 4 days only. 
3 3 iconic techniques by Tortik Annushka in 1!
We start on Monday, July 26. 

Get on board! Link in bio

node.text:
Marble cake ☑️🖤 Guys, we have finally processed all applications for the course and want to inform you that we can add 50 more spaces for our «Technique” course.
All the details how to register for the course you can find by following the link in bio.
Oficcial start of the course is on April 26!
